        <tls:srcline title="鎮州臨濟慧照禪師語錄" target="#KR6q0053_T_001-0499c.58" pos="3">有箇菩提依、涅繫依、解脫依、三身依、境智依、菩薩依、佛依。</tls:srcline>
        <tls:line title="鎮州臨濟慧照禪師語錄 (en)" src="Christoph Anderl">There is this dependent condition called bodhi, the dependent condition called nirvana, the dependent condition of emancipation, the dependent condition of the threefold body, the dependent condition of environment and wisdom, the dependent condition of bodhisattva, the dependent condition of Buddha.</tls:line>
    </tls:text>
